channel.title: Has anyone ever made a decent Electro Swing track on Auxy?
channel.description: Electro Swing has to be my favourite genre but I struggle to make it in Auxy, even though I’m full with ideas! If anyone has made a good sounding ES track, please let me know! I’d love to see how they did it!
